node.text: Swipe 👉🏻 There comes a point in a mans life, when he has an awakening & really realizes what are the most important things to him, that he would die for! This last year was a one hell of a roller coaster for most of us. I decided to start a spiritual journey & connect with God on a deeper level than just belief. I speak to him daily to guide me, so I can be the man, who I know I can be. I’m working hard on stripping my ego, being more vulnerable & transparent, working on self love & becoming a better communicator. This scene from the next episode of #Shahs will show you that side of me again. Enjoy & thank you all for the years of support! Our show would be nothing without you, the loyal fans. We love you!! ♥️🙏
